{
  "doc_id": "29366",
  "text": "The specific higher intracellular expression of NAMPT in GBM was discovered by Reddy et al. in 2008 [33] . Their results also showed that serum extracellular NAMPT levels correlated with tumor grade and was highest in GBM [CITATION_1] . NAMPT inhibitor FK866 induced C6 glioblastoma cell death via inducing autophagic vacuoles, as well as induced nuclei malformation and mitochondria swelling [CITATION_2] . Recently, Tateishi et al. reported that NAMPT inhibitor conferred metabolic susceptibility in IDH1 mutant gliomas [CITATION_3] . The NAMPT inhibitor GMX1778 also enhanced the efficacy of radiolabeled somatostatin analog 177 Lu-DOTATATE treatment and induces a prolonged antitumor response [CITATION_4] .",
